snippet.title: DC Vs Marvel Podcast #90: Cheetah Reveal, Black Widow V2 and Amber Turd?
snippet.description:
Today we talk 

1. What we've been up to 

2. Yelena belova takes over from black widow 

3. Cheetah revealed in ww84 

4. Amber heard vs Johnny Depp gets nasty 

5. Constantine and justice league rebirth in development? 

6. The Boys and Umbrella academy trailers 

7. New batwoman revealed 

8. Neil Gaiman on sandman audiobook and movie 

9. Batman forever Schumacher cut 

10. Kanye West says he will model his white house on "wakanda" 

11. Gambit fan film
